value.name: York council taxpayers to see near-5% rise as budget approved
value.description: Council tax bills in York will go up by nearly 5% from April, the city council has confirmed. The increase, including 2% for social care, was signed off at Thursday's full meeting of City of York Council. It came as the Labour-run council's budget for the next financial year, including a package of cuts worth £14m, was approved.
